	<summary>A web app for reading the Bible with full emphasis on the God`s Word only. Sola scriptura</summary>
	<description>
		<p>Read the Bible with full focus on the text. Over a hundred translations in 29 languages
			are available., bookmarks, reading history, synchronization with different devices,
			different themes, font size and family adjustment, and some other small nice features.</p>
		<p>If you have any additional questions or suggestions - don't be afraid to email me.</p>
		<p>This is FOSS. Here is GitHub -=> https://github.com/Bohooslav/bain.</p>
	</description>
